        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Financing an international education does not have to mean taking on overwhelming debt. Grant Consulting maintains an up-to-date database of scholarships, grants, and financial aid programs offered by universities, governments, and private organizations around the world. We match each student with the funding opportunities that best align with their academic profile, chosen field of study, and destination country.</p>
          <p>Applying for scholarships is competitive, and the difference between winning and losing often comes down to how well the application is prepared. Our consultants guide you through every stage of the process — from identifying the most realistic opportunities to crafting a compelling application strategy that highlights your strengths and sets you apart from other candidates.</p>
          <p>A strong personal statement or motivation essay can make or break a scholarship application. We provide one-on-one essay coaching to help you tell your story in a way that resonates with selection committees. Our team reviews multiple drafts, offers honest feedback, and helps you refine your writing until it clearly communicates your goals, achievements, and potential.</p>
        </div>

